DESCRIPTION:
- You can look up a specific character by using the "scl" command. In this menu, you can check a character's statistics, their Version/3D/GIF variants, as well as their Gen/Fan leaderboards and their "Card ID".
- The "Card ID" is required when submitting images for new "Versions"
CHAR_NOT_FOUND: Could not find the character you are looking for
CHAR_NF_SENSITIVE: No character found. [The `lookup` function is case sensitive!]
NORMAL_DESC: Display the Version variants for this character
ADD_FAN_PTS: Increase your Fan Points for this character
3D_DESC: Displays the 3D variant of a card
GIF_DESC: Displays the GIF variant of a card
NAME: Name
MODAL_TITLE: Enter the amount and currency name
CORRECT_EXAMPLE: Correct format examples: `10 wists`,`3 gems`,`5000 silver`
FAN_PTS_ADDED: `+{{points}}` fan points have been added for: `{{amount}} {{itemName}}`
